{# Baseline agent prompt template.

  Receives a ``prompt.json`` payload in scope. Participants can copy this
  file to a path of their choosing and pass that path to
  ``render_baseline_prompt`` to swap the framing without touching the
  framework code.

  The narrative below mirrors the always-visible block on page 1 of the
  urologist form. Reveal-on-click data (MRI report, pathology report,
  previous notes, family history; for Task 1 also lab panel and PSA
  history) MUST be retrieved via MCP tools — never inlined here.
#}
You are a senior urologist reviewing a patient case. Use the available
tools (radiology / MRI report, pathology report, previous notes, family
history, and — for biopsy decisions — lab panel and PSA history) when you
need to consult a piece of information that isn't in this summary.

Case ID: {{ case_id }}
Task: {{ task }}

Encounter: {{ encounter.department }} on {{ encounter.date }}.
Referrer: {{ encounter.referrer }}.
Type: {{ encounter.type }}.

Headline values (always visible at the start of the consult):
  - {{ patient.age }}-year-old male
  - PSA {{ current_psa.value }} ng/mL{% if current_psa.date %} (drawn {{ current_psa.date }}){% endif %}

Vitals: {% set v = patient.vitals -%}
{%- set parts = [] -%}
{%- if v.weight %}{% set _ = parts.append('weight ' ~ v.weight) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.height %}{% set _ = parts.append('height ' ~ v.height) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.bmi %}{% set _ = parts.append('BMI ' ~ v.bmi) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.bp %}{% set _ = parts.append('BP ' ~ v.bp) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if v.hr %}{% set _ = parts.append('HR ' ~ v.hr) %}{% endif -%}
{{ parts | join(', ') if parts else 'not recorded' }}.
{% if v.smoking %}Smoking: {{ v.smoking }}.{% endif %}

Allergies: {{ patient.allergies | join(', ') if patient.allergies else 'NKA' }}.
Active medication: {{ patient.medication or 'none recorded' }}.
Problem list / PMHx: {{ patient.pmhx | join(', ') if patient.pmhx else 'none recorded' }}.

{% for section in note_sections -%}
{{ section.s }}: {{ section.t }}

{% endfor -%}

{% set s = patient.social -%}
{%- set social_parts = [] -%}
{%- if s.occupation %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(s.occupation) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if s.marital %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(s.marital) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if s.living %}{% set _ = social_parts.append(s.living) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if social_parts %}Patient info: {{ social_parts | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}
{%- if s.next_of_kin %}
Next of kin: {{ s.next_of_kin }}.{% endif %}

{% set lf = patient.lifestyle -%}
{%- set lf_parts = [] -%}
{%- if lf.alcohol %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append('alcohol ' ~ lf.alcohol) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if lf.exercise %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append('exercise ' ~ lf.exercise) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if lf.ipss %}{% set _ = lf_parts.append(lf.ipss) %}{% endif -%}
{%- if lf_parts %}Lifestyle: {{ lf_parts | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}

{% if recent_other %}Recent other appointments: {{ recent_other | join('; ') }}.{% endif %}
{% if admin %}Admin: {{ admin }}{% endif %}

{% if labs %}
Lab panel (already in hand at this consult):
{% for l in labs %}  - {{ l.name }}: {{ l.val }}{% if l.flag %} [{{ l.flag }}]{% endif %} ({{ l.date }})
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if psa_trend %}
PSA history (already in hand at this consult):
{% for p in psa_trend %}  - {{ p.date }}: {{ p.val }} ng/mL
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

Information you can request via tools (mirroring what the urologist would
order or actively elicit during the consult):
  - radiology / MRI report (PI-RADS, prostate volume, PSA density, AI csPCa probability)
  - pathology report ({{ 'Gleason / ISUP / cores / growth pattern / PNI / LVI / AI-predicted ISUP' if task == 'risk_stratification' else 'biopsy results if available' }})
  - previous GP / urology consultation notes
  - family history of prostate cancer (anamnesis){% if task != 'risk_stratification' %}
  - lab panel
  - PSA history trend{% endif %}

